    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i've heard some people say that it's actually good for the local economy though, because workers having more money means they spend more at places like my shop. is there any real evidence for that side of it, or is it mostly just an idea?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
