    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so when you say it's mostly a theory \"promoted by progressive economists,\" it sounds like you think the math doesn't really hold up for someone in my position. if i'm looking at my budget, does the data actually support the idea that this helps, or is it basically just an ideological move that ignores the reality of small business owners?",
